<br>
He is unbelieveable experience at level 24, slightly more than a bubble an hour, totally risk free if you watch yourself.<br>
<br>
Interesting side note however: through the entirety of 4 bubbles of exp i did there last night, not a single malise EVER stuck to him. I found it much more productive to launch in with a nice shock of steel and then run around like a sissy until root stuck again. if he EVER got me down two three bubbles left without being rooted, i zoned as fast as possible. Very easy to do since the pathing makes him take forever to get out. Ran Flamespinner will not clean him off of you if you run to the library so hence the need to zone. Only had this happen once.<br>
<br>
Remember: if youre trying to run out of the cell, click the door while its open to make it close. When i had to run it was pretty freakish standing there the full duration waiting for the door to close thinking i could squeeze into the gap there.<br>
<br>
One other thing. Osargen dropped ice of vellious three times in the hours i was there. aside from that he is totally lootless, best youll get is a few gold off of the prisoners when you clean them out.<br>
<br>
most excellent spawn<br>
<br>
